caption.title: NS1 antigen strips.
caption.p: Immunochromatographic assay for DENV NS1Ag test for real time RT-PCR positive samples (29, 42, 50 and 73). Two samples (22 and 127) that were negative by real time RT-PCR were included for validation. a. Arrowhead: positive band; b. * indicates the four patient samples found to be positive.
